      • getSource

        public java.lang.String getSource()
        Gets the source. Source language in two letter language code. Use the five letter code when clarifying between multiple supported languages. When model_id is used directly, it will override the source-target language combination. Also, when a two letter language code is used, but no suitable default is found, it returns an error.
        Returns:
        the source
